    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Beetle that feeds on cotton buds and flowers. Thought to be native to Central America, it migrated into the United States from Mexico in the late 19th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
